data.description: Welcome home to 103 Live Oak Way in Taylors!!!  This lovely brick ranch, that is sitting on 0.8 acres, in the well-established Oak Wood Acres subdivision, is ready to welcome its new homeowner.  The first thing you will notice is the size of the lot...WOW...it is very large with a fenced in yard and a HUGE 3 car detached garage/workshop for all your hobbies/car needs.  Can you say man cave?  When you walk in the front door you will be greeted by the enormous dining room.  This is the perfect space to have your large family/friend gatherings.  The dining room is open to the kitchen which flows right into the oversized living room.  These are the perfect spaces to host.  All three bedrooms and two bathrooms are located just down the hall from the kitchen.  This home is approximately 13 minutes from downtown Greer and 16 minutes from downtown Greenville.  You will not want to miss this opportunity.
